44Ac 3:11 While he was holding on to Peter and John, all the people came running to them in what was called "Solomon's Colonnade". They were dumbfounded.
44Ac 3:12 When Peter saw this, he said to the people£º "Fellow Israelites, why are you wondering about this, and why are you staring at us as if by our own power or godliness we made him walk - 
