45Rm 16:8 Greet Ampliatus, my dear friend in the Lord.
45Rm 16:9 Greet Urbanus, our co-worker in the Messiah, and my dear friend Stachys.
45Rm 16:10 Greet Apelles, who has been approved by the Messiah. Greet those who belong to the family of Aristobulus.
45Rm 16:11 Greet Herodion, my fellow Jew. Greet those in the family of Narcissus, who belong to the Lord.
45Rm 16:12 Greet Tryphaena and Tryphosa, who have worked hard for the Lord. Greet my dear friend Persis, who has toiled diligently for the Lord.
