49Eph 1:14 who is the guarantee of our inheritance until God redeems his own possession for his praise and glory. 
49Eph 1:15 Therefore, because I have heard about your faith in the Lord Jesus and your love for all the saints,
49Eph 1:16 I never stop giving thanks for you as I mention you in my prayers.
49Eph 1:17 I pray that the God of our Lord Jesus, the Messiah, the most glorious Father, would give you a wise spirit, along with revelation that comes through knowing the Messiah fully.
49Eph 1:18 Then, with the eyes of your hearts enlightened, you will know the confidence that is produced by God having called you, the rich glory that is his inheritance among the saints,
