49Eph 3:10 He did this so that now, through the church, the wisdom of God in all its variety might be made known to the rulers and authorities in the heavenly realm
49Eph 3:11 in keeping with the eternal purpose that God carried out through the Messiah Jesus our Lord,
49Eph 3:12 in whom we have boldness and confident access through his faithfulness.
49Eph 3:13 So then, I ask you not to become discouraged because of my troubles on your behalf, which work toward your glory.39
49Eph 3:14 This is the reason I bow my knees before the Father of our Lord Jesus, the Messiah,
49Eph 3:15 from whom every family in heaven and on earth receives its name.
49Eph 3:16 I pray that he would give you, according to his glorious riches, strength in your inner being and power through his Spirit,
49Eph 3:17 and that the Messiah would make his home in your hearts through faith. Then, having been rooted and grounded in love,
49Eph 3:18 you will be able to understand, along with all the saints, what is wide, long, high, and deep - 
